---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service | WV Wild Outdoors"
  description="Terms of service for WV Wild Outdoors website usage."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-brand-cream min-h-screen py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-8 md:p-12">

        <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-brand-brown mb-8">
          Terms of Service
        </h1>

        <p class="text-stone-500 mb-8">
          Last updated: December 11, 2025
        </p>

        <div class="prose prose-stone max-w-none">

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Welcome to WV Wild Outdoors
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            By using this website, you agree to these terms. WV Wild Outdoors operates
            a physical retail store in Birch River, West Virginia. This website provides
            information about our store and services.
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Website Use
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            This website is for informational purposes only. We do not currently sell
            products online. All purchases must be made in person at our physical location.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-stone-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Product availability and prices shown are subject to change without notice</li>
            <li>Images are for illustration purposes and may not reflect actual inventory</li>
            <li>Contact us to confirm availability before visiting</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Firearm Sales & Transfers
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            WV Wild Outdoors is a licensed Federal Firearms Licensee (FFL). All firearm
            sales and transfers are conducted in accordance with:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-stone-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Federal firearms laws and ATF regulations</li>
            <li>West Virginia state firearms laws</li>
            <li>Required background check procedures (NICS)</li>
            <li>Proper identification and documentation requirements</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            We reserve the right to refuse any sale or transfer at our discretion.
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Age Requirements
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            Federal law requires the following minimum ages for firearm purchases:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-stone-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>18 years or older</strong> for rifles and shotguns (long guns)</li>
            <li><strong>21 years or older</strong> for handguns</li>
            <li>Valid government-issued photo ID required for all purchases</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            What to Bring for Firearm Purchases
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            To purchase a firearm at WV Wild Outdoors, you'll need:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-stone-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Valid government-issued photo ID</strong> with your current address (driver's license, state ID, or passport with proof of address)</li>
            <li>Ability to complete <a href="https://www.atf.gov/firearms/firearms-forms" class="text-brand-orange hover:underline">ATF Form 4473</a> in person</li>
            <li>Time to wait for the NICS background check (usually same-day for West Virginia residents)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4 text-sm">
            For more information about federal firearms requirements, visit
            <a href="https://www.atf.gov/firearms" class="text-brand-orange hover:underline">ATF.gov/firearms</a>.
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Returns & Refunds - Firearms
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            All firearm sales at WV Wild Outdoors are final once the transfer is complete.
            Once you take possession of a firearm after completing ATF Form 4473 and passing
            the NICS background check, the sale cannot be reversed.
          </p>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            If you change your mind before the transfer is complete, please let us know.
            Background check fees are non-refundable once the NICS check is initiated.
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Hunting & Fishing Licenses
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            As an authorized WV DNR license agent, we sell West Virginia hunting and
            fishing licenses. License sales are governed by WV Division of Natural
            Resources regulations.
          </p>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            <strong>Licenses are non-transferable.</strong> Under
            <a href="https://code.wvlegislature.gov/20-2-36/" class="text-brand-orange hover:underline">WV Code ยง20-2-36</a>,
            it is unlawful to transfer a license to another person.
          </p>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            Lost or damaged licenses can be replaced for a $1 fee. Please double-check
            your license type before completing your purchase.
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Contact Form Submissions
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            When you submit a contact form:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-stone-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li>We will respond as soon as reasonably possible</li>
            <li>Response times may vary based on business hours and volume</li>
            <li>Form submissions do not guarantee product availability or pricing</li>
            <li>We are not responsible for delays in electronic communication</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Intellectual Property
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            All content on this website, including text, images, logos, and design,
            is owned by WV Wild Outdoors or used with permission. You may not copy,
            reproduce, or distribute our content without written permission.
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Limitation of Liability
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            This website is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. WV Wild
            Outdoors is not liable for any damages arising from your use of this website
            or reliance on information provided here.
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Governing Law
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            These terms are governed by the laws of the State of West Virginia. Any
            disputes will be resolved in the courts of Nicholas County, West Virginia.
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Changes to Terms
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            We may update these terms from time to time. Changes will be posted on
            this page with an updated revision date.
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-brown mt-8 mb-4">
            Contact Us
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            Questions about these terms? Contact us at:
          </p>
          <address class="not-italic text-stone-600 mb-6">
            <p><strong>WV Wild Outdoors</strong></p>
            <p>121 Birch River Rd</p>
            <p>Birch River, WV 26610</p>
            <p>Phone: (304) 649-2607</p>
          </address>

        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
